review: really great food and amazing cheesecake great date night spot

Lousey food....sugar overload from the cheesecake. The manager, Tom is not good. Never came back to my table to address a problem. Found something in my food. Didn't feel good all day from their low quality food. Overpriced and underserved. Never going back again.
A good place for drinks and dessert, the food is not exactly what I would call heart and/or stomach friendly. I usually regret eating meals here.
